This was done in sprint one by accident.
Through the process of completing our sprint goal, we realised this had also been finished.

"As a virtual reality researcher, i need a form that saves a participant id number along side their name, so that i can refer to both of them in my analysis"
label: Deliver Next (Low Risk/High Value)
Moscow: Should
Story Points: 2

Background:  When researchers come to sharing their results it can be necessary to refer to individual cases, as far as data protection is concerned it is
better to be able to refer to participants using a participant ID rather than by name.
